						               													<description>A semi-cooperative board game of terror and violent survival. Inspired by the greatest works of horror, Carnage is a game driven by your choices and your ability to survive against deadly traps, madmen and even your friends. For 2 to 6 players from 14 years old. Filled with Easter eggs from popular horror movies, old and recent, this is a must for the lovers of the genre. There are tons of references to slashers, psychopaths and other villains as well as iconic locations and items.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Each player gets 4 actions to spend during a turn.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;To win: &amp;#10;1. Complete your personal objective&amp;#10;2. Start the power in the Engine Room&amp;#10;3. Unlock the door to the Control Room&amp;#10;4. Get out&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Highlights&amp;#10;1. Simple gameplay for an instant immersive experience, while complex in its variables for a great replayability. &amp;#10;2. Play certain cards at ANY time, including when you are not the active player. &amp;#10;3. Get through twisted and deadly traps that will certainly test your nerves.&amp;#10;4. Embrace your madness and take advantage of it if you would lose your sanity.&amp;#10;5. If you die, you now play as a Deranged to hunt and kill the other players.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
